00:35:55.360 --> 00:36:00.620
If you had no idea what a potluck
dinner was, you might think it's

00:36:00.620 --> 00:36:05.280
with a big pot outside or
something on a campfire,

00:36:05.280 --> 00:36:09.290
and maybe people just bring
whatever they want and throw it in

00:36:09.290 --> 00:36:14.150
and you hope you get lucky with
a delicious meal, but a lot

00:36:14.150 --> 00:36:15.950
of people won't know what that is.

00:36:15.950 --> 00:36:21.070
I explained to folks that a potluck
dinner is basically a dinner

00:36:21.070 --> 00:36:24.660
where people each bring a
dish and everyone shares.

00:36:25.670 --> 00:36:28.210
If you want to use stuff like
that, just explain it.

00:36:30.190 --> 00:36:34.820
Provide context for images and
stories, and then explain acronyms,

00:36:34.820 --> 00:36:38.580
