lived experience, we're pros.

00:38:04.690 --> 00:38:07.320
We know what it feels like
inside our body, we know

00:38:07.320 --> 00:38:11.350
what it feels like to
deal with inaccessibility.

00:38:11.350 --> 00:38:17.070
Our voices matter and we need more
disabled folks out there kicking ass,

00:38:17.070 --> 00:38:21.960
and being vocal about
our lived experiences.

